node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 20, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, sky and text that says 'WHEN WE LOSE SOMEONE WE LOVE, WE MUST LEARN NOT TO LIVE WITHOUT THEM, BUT TO LIVE WITH THE LOVE THEY LEFT BEHIND.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 20, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Be grateful and be positive, because life is too short to always be worried. Let go of the stress and realize you're blessed. P.T'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The world is a reflection of you.'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 19, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Don't quit. Sometimes the things you are hoping for, come at unexpected times.'.

May be an image of text that says 'Not everyone thinks the way you think, knows the things you know, believes the things you believe, nor acts the way you would act. Remember this and you will go a long way in getting along with people. -Arthur Forman-'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 17, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, flower and text that says 'You either get bitter or you get better. It's that simple. You either take what has been dealt to you and allow it to make you a better person, or you allow it to tear you down. The choice does not belong to fate, it belongs to you.'.
